metadata.name: A skull of line #0
metadata.description:
Immortality,
sacrifice, and death.

With sacrifice comes valor, and valor brings self-devotion, and with self-devotion, comes death...
So I'll never fall on my knees!

This drawing is a mixture of scribbles and Persian calligraphy.

The translation of calligraphy text:
"I'll never kneel"

This is my first artwork on Foundation. Some of the money made from this NFT will be donated to a charity to help children with cancer.

Time spent on this NFT Art: 3 weeks
Software: Sketchbook
Gadget: Galaxy Note 9
